This result illustrates the more general connection between Bayes correlated
 equilibrium and Bayes Nash equilibrium for all information structures studied
 in Bergemann and Morris (2016 TE), where we showed that a joint distribution
 over actions and states is Bayes correlated equilibrium if and only if
 it forms a Bayes Nash equilibrium distribution under some information structure.
